text: Aristolochia thwaitesii is a species of plant in the family Aristolochiaceae. It is endemic to China. ==References== * China Plant Specialist Group 2004. Aristolochia thwaitesii. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. Downloaded on 20 August 2007.
